# Root build context ignore (used by deploy/Dockerfile, whose context is the repo root).
# Keeps host build artifacts — especially web/node_modules and the SQLite data — out of the image.
**/node_modules
**/bin
**/obj
**/dist
**/.vite
**/.git
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/App_Data
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.user
**/npm-debug.log
